{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"linux下包安装\"><a href=\"#linux%E4%B8%8B%E5%8C%85%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>linux下包安装</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>下载<br>\n从<a href=\"https://www.mongodb.com/download-center#community\">官网下载</a> linux 包\n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 690px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 51.13421550094518%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"download\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/download-7ea2588056a93f0eb77d0e1841f97ba2-44d6a.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/download-7ea2588056a93f0eb77d0e1841f97ba2-f4799.png 173w,\n/static/download-7ea2588056a93f0eb77d0e1841f97ba2-b3b1d.png 345w,\n/static/download-7ea2588056a93f0eb77d0e1841f97ba2-44d6a.png 690w,\n/static/download-7ea2588056a93f0eb77d0e1841f97ba2-bc0f7.png 1035w,\n/static/download-7ea2588056a93f0eb77d0e1841f97ba2-54245.png 1058w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>解压,安装</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">tar</span> -xvzf mongodb-linux-x86_64-3.2.10.tgz\n$ <span class=\"token function\">mv</span> mongodb-linux-x86_64-3.2.10 /usr/local/mongodb</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<ul>\n<li>MongoDB 的可执行文件, bin 目录下，将其添加到 PATH 路径中</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">export</span> PATH<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/usr/local/mongodb/bin:<span class=\"token variable\">$PATH</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>  为当前用户添加</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ vim ~/.bash_profile</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>  然后, insert 即可</p>\n<ul>\n<li>新建数据库目录</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> -p /data/db</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h1 id=\"mongodb-启动\"><a href=\"#mongodb-%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>mongodb 启动</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ mongod</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<ul>\n<li>启动异常(Attempt to create a lock file on a read-only directory: /data/db),</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">chown</span> -R 当前用户名 /data/db/</code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"linux下包安装 下载 从 官网下载  linux 包\n 解压,安装 MongoDB 的可执行文件, bin 目录下，将其添加到 PATH 路径中   为当前用户添加   然后, insert 即可 新建数据库目录 mongodb 启动 启动异常(Attempt to…","frontmatter":{"title":"mongodb安装","cover":null,"date":"2017-10-19T08:00:00.000Z","category":"mongodb","tags":["mongodb"]},"fields":{"nextTitle":"promise","nextSlug":"/javascript/promise/promise/","prevTitle":"内存泄露","prevSlug":"/javascript/memory-leak/memoryLeak/","slug":"/mongodb/mongodb/","date":"2017-10-18T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/mongodb/mongodb/"}}